Top Stories (February 21)

CALIFORNIA SENATE PANEL PASSES $1.0265 ENERGY PROGRAM BILL
The California Senate Appropriations Committee in a vote Wednesday passed a 
bill (Senate Bill 1x 5) that would allow for $1.0265 billion to fund 
low-income, distributed generation and energy efficiency programs. The bill 
now goes to the Senate floor.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/bridgene
ws/2001/02/21/eng-bridgenews_8883/eng-bridgenews_8883_201200_159_428042066284

CALIFORNIA POWER WOES COULD HELP WISCONSIN ENERGY BUILD PLANTS
California's deregulation-related power troubles are helping smooth a path 
for Wisconsin Energy Corp.'s massive $6 billion plan to build and upgrade 
power plants in Wisconsin, an analyst said Wednesday.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/21/eng-djn/eng-djn_204025_153_713997979648

DUKE WON'T SIGN POWER DEALS IN CALIFORNIA UNTIL UTILITIES PAY DEBT
One major power supplier said it won't sign long-term power supply contracts 
with California until the company is assured it will be paid hundreds of 
millions of dollars owed by two of the state's nearly bankrupt utilities.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/21/eng-djn/eng-djn_002031_130_557335063349

SCOTTISHPOWER US UNIT GETS OREGON GRANT TO UP PRICES 3%
U.K electricity firm ScottishPower PLC (SPI) said Wednesday that its U.S. 
subsidiary PacifiCorp (X.PCP) has received approval from the Oregon Public 
Utility Commission for a 3% overall price increase, equivalent to $22.8 
million.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
02/21/eng-djn/eng-djn_074028_59_1793858073652

DANOIL ENERGY LTD - SIGNS DEFINITIVE MERGER AGREEMENT
Danoil Energy Ltd. announced that it has signed a Definitive Agreement with 
Western Facilities Fund (WFF) and Nevis Ltd., providing for the 
implementation of the previously announced combination of the parties' 
respective assets and operations.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/comtex/2
